title: KL2020: Terug in de Lucht
overview: What does KLM do to survive the Covid-19 pandemic? And how will they find their path to recovery? In KL2020: Terug in de Lucht ten KLM employees will tell their personal story. From towing service to management, from the cabin to operations: despite everything, the involvement and enthusiasm of the staff remains unabated. At the same time, their experiences are recognizable to many.
